      "summary": "<p>Kamal Mouzawak, founder of Souk el-Tayeb</p>",
      "introduction": "<p>Kamal Mouzawak is the founder of Souk el-Tayeb, the Tawlet restaurant in Mar Mikhaël, and several guesthouses, known as Beit, scattered throughout Lebanon. He is also the author of several books, including: « Delights of the Thousand and One Nights » (2012) ; Lebanese Home Cooking (2015), and Manger libanais (2017).</p>",
